{"tid":490635,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"耀才證券控胡孟青誹謗","createTime":"2017-12-05T20:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T02:46:01.000Z","uid":76855,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c015e2e819c8a03cc43fa7d66c1d5a37d22c598e","tid":490635,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T20:34:25.000Z","msg":"耀才證券入稟高院，控告著名股評人胡孟青誹謗。耀才證券指胡於上月13日在新城電台節目「開市直擊」中談及當時新股「雷蛇」時，虛假指出耀才證券的暗盤買賣網頁失靈無法進行交易，並指耀才證券當日暗盤每股「雷蛇」的成交價可高達6元，並於節目中反問另外一位主持人耀才證券的競爭對手輝立證券每股「4個零5蚊」，是否才屬「正常價」。<br />\n<br />\n耀才證券認為胡發佈失實訊息，於入稟狀中澄清當日網站並沒有失靈，亦指胡與輝立證券董事黃瑋傑相熟，遂特意發放虛假消息詆毀耀才證券。<br />\n`<br />\n原告耀才證券國際香港有限公司要求胡孟青賠償及停止再發佈有關言論，並需於網上刪除相關文章及節目。"},{"pid":"657207d827b46ac2320644a028e6b10ad1f7e118","tid":490635,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d9c8b9b30b447152572a0ab81eac9529c25a20","tid":490635,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"睇戲"},{"pid":"4139d74c292785c40bb1bd3fb3bed24736029827","tid":490635,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n財演"},{"pid":"93e37be2c198d2381fde282fa900c029508094eb","tid":490635,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678db6f1a04d214f0697813511e6a0087be4574a","tid":490635,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco